SONOMA AND MENDOCINO VALLEYS

Until recently, the vineyards of Sonoma, only one row of hills to the east, languished without the recognition enjoyed by the Napa wineries for decades. Most of their good wines were sold in bulk to prestigious names in Napa or Santa Clara Valleys. This has all changed. Some of California's best wines are now produced in Sonoma or Mendocino. We happily present the best wines and vineyards of this important wine-growing area to the wine drinkers of New York.
